{"questionId":"ba06b998-d854-4b29-830c-15d877280c75_4","correctAnswer":"24","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Apply the factoring from the given condition","content":"Note $56+8x = 8(7+x)$, and $7+x=3$."},{"title":"Compute the target value","content":"So $56+8x = 8 \\cdot 3 = 24$. The answer is <strong>24</strong>."}]}